{"tid":859007,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭民望新低","createTime":"2018-10-12T08:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T12:17:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"100f6d0403166b4a1e62dc03c9f609a8aa94c608","tid":859007,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181012/20520449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F20520449&d=yJVT0z9mqF5dDCmKlzSFzkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=729de77d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F20520449&h=1a88c2ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181012/20520449</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月12日 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181012/large/1010davies3007b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1010davies3007b.jpg&h=c368d7b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【港大民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】林鄭月娥前日發表任內第二份《施政報告》後，民意評分大幅倒退。港大民研民調發現林鄭最新支持度較月初顯著下跌4.7分至47.6分，是其上任以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n施政報告滿意度插水<br />\n<br />\n前日公佈的《施政報告》提出「明日大嶼願景」發展計劃，惹來社會反對。香港大學民意研究計劃前晚訪問584名香港巿民，對比2017年《施政報告》，發現市民的滿意率由去年的47.5%跌至33.3%，不滿意率則由去年的13.9%上升至34.1%，淨滿意率則由去年的33.6百分點，大幅暴跌至負0.8個百分點，滿意率淨值是14年以來第三低。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥民望亦受挫，支持度和支持率淨值均創上任以來新低。林鄭支持度較10月初顯著下跌4.7分，至47.6分，支持率淨值更由正轉負，由正4個百分點跌至負10個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n此外，撇除不清楚施政報告的受訪者後，民調發現23%受訪者稱在施政報告發表後對香港前途信心增加，45%表示信心減少，前途信心效應淨值為負22個百分點，較去年低43個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n■記者曾偉龍  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n聶德權稱暫不重啟政改<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n九價HPV疫苗　小五女童免費打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林超英斥低估風暴潮威脅<br />\n<br />\n向內地買海砂料花439億<br />\n<br />\n稱藉「玫瑰園」鑑古知今<br />\n<br />\nLego林鄭倒錢落海<br />\n<br />\n紅隧加價一倍　政府死不修改<br />\n<br />\n特首自詡大膽：禁傳統煙有得諗<br />\n<br />\n聶德權稱暫不重啟政改<br />\n<br />\n九價HPV疫苗　小五女童免費打<br />\n<br />\n產檢毋須假紙可獲有薪病假<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄：普教中交學校決定<br />\n<br />\n天價填海　林鄭卸責規劃署"},{"pid":"0dc6fb8a519ec7fc264f8f1b0751cc6cdea468f3","tid":859007,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1f035b72beff1e91474f48af037da15dc0c8ada","tid":859007,"uid":88663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0dc6fb8a519ec7fc264f8f1b0751cc6cdea468f3","tid":859007,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"邊一個傳媒？亂up左啲乜？"},{"pid":"db7e5e493c544d4d7f76a5821b4a8d2b37a76ac7","tid":859007,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57K6g5o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57K6g5o.gif&h=b66b4e1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"352ba9282c25c4689a33f77b12c5c8ddfb51fe8a","tid":859007,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19c615fa05a8910adb032322f95dac3ff17d251","tid":859007,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"收到消息,呢份施政報告會令林鄭民望標高#lol# <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Oq7yZRXt1I4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOq7yZRXt1I4&d=yJVT0z9mqF5dDCmKlzSFzkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=8d87ac5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Oq7yZRXt1I4</a><br />\n3:55開始"}]}